{"tid":217752,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"生日飯去邊食好??","createTime":"2017-04-26T04:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T15:01:11.000Z","uid":69159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"75e3afa9fcf4161956bf1dd2ced30e5e69a3680c","tid":217752,"uid":69159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:24:04.000Z","msg":"自己幫自己慶祝<br />\n同屋企人食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n價位&lt;250一位<br />\n3個人食<br />\n<br />\n除左打邊爐都可以<br />\n集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66318b96b6b5fd1ee89949ff4bf6684c2da742e3","tid":217752,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:24:55.000Z","msg":"求其啦"},{"pid":"e653a13fec189509edf76f187d8ea8c2da4cc1d2","tid":217752,"uid":72554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:26:31.000Z","msg":"中餐？西餐？日燒？"},{"pid":"329374fefdc8c48453122de34e4b8128699d10ea","tid":217752,"uid":72554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:41:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中餐？西餐？日燒？</blockquote><br />\n中推介：紅磡冰室<br />\n小炒平均6x一個有湯有嘢飲<br />\n味道唔錯 推介尖沙咀金馬倫道嗰間<br />\n如果筆直高少少 可以行前少少去霸王山莊食<br />\n<br />\n西推介：風車/m18唔係好記得個名<br />\n食扒有飯有麵有前菜<br />\n兩間都係大圍<br />\n平均都係150左右一位<br />\n味道都ok 氣氛都好<br />\n但係唔好遇着球賽！好L多人<br />\n一多人個味道就下降<br />\n<br />\n日推介：牛角<br />\n如果＄250一個咁應該要食放題<br />\n可以揀放題／散叫（想食好野一定散叫）<br />\n利申未食個放題 但係平時嘅味道唔錯<br />\n我記得放題有和牛 牛 雞 豬 飯 麵 甜品<br />\n其實都好抵 氣氛都唔錯唔會太嘈<br />\n除非有人爭埋單 之後嘈交 仲撕爛銀紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d621e0559e42653258f9b9fcfb9d17522c9fafa2","tid":217752,"uid":72554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:43:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中餐？西餐？日燒？</blockquote><br />\n中推介：紅磡冰室<br />\n小炒平均6x一個有湯有嘢飲<br />\n味道唔錯 推介尖沙咀金馬倫道嗰間<br />\n如果筆直